1
00:00:12,520 --> 00:00:14,120
We are just using each other.

2
00:00:15,920 --> 00:00:16,880
Yes.

3
00:00:17,680 --> 00:00:20,400
I help you get revenge on Gu Licheng and his wife,

4
00:00:20,400 --> 00:00:23,320
and you help me get the position of Minister of Revenue.

5
00:00:23,320 --> 00:00:26,380
But right now, Gu Licheng and his wife are still useful.

6
00:00:26,480 --> 00:00:28,400
So you can't kill them.

7
00:00:29,720 --> 00:00:31,240
I don't need you to tell me what to do.

8
00:00:31,240 --> 00:00:32,080
Don't forget

9
00:00:33,960 --> 00:00:36,200
who gave you this life,

10
00:00:36,480 --> 00:00:37,640
this face,

11
00:00:38,000 --> 00:00:40,260
and your current status as the God of War.

12
00:00:40,520 --> 00:00:42,920
I can take everything back at any time

13
00:00:43,640 --> 00:00:46,240
and make you a dead man again.

14
00:00:48,400 --> 00:00:50,330
I don't care about wealth or death.

15
00:00:51,640 --> 00:00:53,440
I just want to know one thing.

16
00:00:53,960 --> 00:00:55,040
Is Mu Jiuyun

17
00:00:55,880 --> 00:00:57,120
really dead?

18
00:00:58,160 --> 00:00:59,480
Mu Jiuyun

19
00:01:00,480 --> 00:01:01,880
is really dead.

20
00:01:08,760 --> 00:01:10,690
You'd better be telling the truth.

21
00:01:11,320 --> 00:01:12,600
Otherwise,

22
00:01:12,880 --> 00:01:14,200
your fate

23
00:01:14,680 --> 00:01:17,120
will be worse than Gu Licheng and his wife.

24
00:01:25,600 --> 00:01:27,920
Why does Su Cheng have the jade pendant?

25
00:01:28,520 --> 00:01:30,360
Could A'yu still be alive?

26
00:01:31,240 --> 00:01:32,840
I must find out the truth.

27
00:01:50,039 --> 00:01:50,960
Princess.

28
00:02:02,480 --> 00:02:03,480
Where

29
00:02:03,840 --> 00:02:05,160
are you going?

30
00:02:10,280 --> 00:02:12,040
Where I go is my own business.

31
00:02:12,160 --> 00:02:13,120
Leave me alone.

32
00:02:15,400 --> 00:02:16,640
Wherever you go,

33
00:02:16,920 --> 00:02:17,960
I won't stop you.

34
00:02:18,720 --> 00:02:20,780
You just need to answer one question.

35
00:02:24,520 --> 00:02:26,280
If you want to kill me, just do it.

36
00:02:26,280 --> 00:02:27,320
Cut the crap.

37
00:02:27,320 --> 00:02:27,960
Tell me.

38
00:02:29,280 --> 00:02:30,600
This jade pendant,

39
00:02:31,560 --> 00:02:32,840
is it yours?

40
00:02:40,320 --> 00:02:42,600
Why is it backfiring now of all times?

41
00:02:42,840 --> 00:02:45,440
I've taken several pills over the past three days.

42
00:02:45,440 --> 00:02:47,440
Can my body not take it anymore?

43
00:02:51,400 --> 00:02:52,800
This jade pendant

44
00:02:53,800 --> 00:02:54,760
is mine.

45
00:02:54,760 --> 00:02:55,600
It is you.

46
00:02:57,560 --> 00:02:58,800
What is it to you?

47
00:03:04,560 --> 00:03:05,480
What's wrong?

48
00:03:08,960 --> 00:03:11,520
He is in cahoots with Gu Licheng and Mu Yujiao.

49
00:03:11,840 --> 00:03:13,240
I can't say.

50
00:03:18,840 --> 00:03:20,240
There's no one else here.

51
00:03:20,880 --> 00:03:22,520
You don't need to pretend.

52
00:03:23,600 --> 00:03:25,040
This jade pendant

53
00:03:25,520 --> 00:03:27,680
was given to me by a woman.

54
00:03:28,280 --> 00:03:30,740
When I was on my way to the marriage alliance,

55
00:03:30,960 --> 00:03:33,160
I met a man and a woman under the cliff.

56
00:03:33,800 --> 00:03:35,200
The man was already dead.

57
00:03:35,760 --> 00:03:37,920
The woman was taking her last breath.

58
00:03:39,800 --> 00:03:41,460
She gave me this jade pendant,

59
00:03:43,000 --> 00:03:45,260
hoping that I would bury her and her lover

60
00:03:45,480 --> 00:03:46,640
together.

61
00:03:53,840 --> 00:03:54,880
You may go.

62
00:04:30,680 --> 00:04:32,600
What exactly is Mo Yu planning?

63
00:04:33,440 --> 00:04:34,440
Never mind.

64
00:04:34,440 --> 00:04:36,040
I must find Su Cheng quickly.

65
00:04:36,240 --> 00:04:40,170
The Emperor's oral decree summons the Princess of Beidi to the palace.

66
00:04:44,880 --> 00:04:46,720
Knowing Mo Yu's personality,

67
00:04:47,000 --> 00:04:49,360
why would he defend her time and time again?

68
00:04:49,360 --> 00:04:51,440
Has he taken a fancy to this bitch?

69
00:04:51,440 --> 00:04:52,680
It seems counting on Mo Yu

70
00:04:52,680 --> 00:04:54,000
to get rid of her for us

71
00:04:54,000 --> 00:04:55,440
is impossible.

72
00:04:56,080 --> 00:04:57,360
Not only that.

73
00:04:57,800 --> 00:05:00,260
Pillow talk is the hardest to guard against.

74
00:05:00,480 --> 00:05:02,520
If we let her stay by Mo Yu's side,

75
00:05:02,800 --> 00:05:06,040
I'm afraid the ones he will eliminate in the future

76
00:05:06,040 --> 00:05:07,000
will be us.

77
00:05:07,200 --> 00:05:08,480
Then what should we do?

78
00:05:09,120 --> 00:05:10,560
Our only plan now

79
00:05:11,480 --> 00:05:13,440
is to strike first.

80
00:05:19,640 --> 00:05:21,100
Greetings, Your Majesty.

81
00:05:21,520 --> 00:05:22,650
Greetings, Mother.

82
00:05:22,880 --> 00:05:23,560
At ease.

83
00:05:23,560 --> 00:05:26,000
I have heard that the Great Jin governs the world with rites and music,

84
00:05:26,000 --> 00:05:27,400
and educates the people.

85
00:05:27,400 --> 00:05:29,360
My daughter has only recently married into the Great Jin,

86
00:05:29,360 --> 00:05:31,520
and she is already so well-mannered.

87
00:05:31,520 --> 00:05:33,280
You are too polite, Your Majesty of Northern Di.

88
00:05:33,280 --> 00:05:35,000
Northern Di is rich in resources

89
00:05:35,000 --> 00:05:36,440
and has honest people.

90
00:05:36,440 --> 00:05:37,880
For our Great Jin to have such an ally

91
00:05:37,880 --> 00:05:39,720
is truly a blessing for the people.

92
00:05:39,720 --> 00:05:40,480
Daughter,

93
00:05:40,760 --> 00:05:42,360
I came here this time

94
00:05:42,360 --> 00:05:44,040
firstly to see you,

95
00:05:44,040 --> 00:05:47,970
and secondly to discuss the alliance with the Emperor of the Great Jin.

96
00:05:48,120 --> 00:05:50,880
The Vice Minister of Revenue has arrived.

97
00:05:57,480 --> 00:06:00,740
Vice Minister of Revenue, Gu Licheng, greets Your Majesty

98
00:06:00,920 --> 00:06:02,450
and the King of Northern Di.

99
00:06:02,920 --> 00:06:04,520
At ease, my beloved subject.

100
00:06:07,080 --> 00:06:08,680
So the Princess is here too.

101
00:06:09,120 --> 00:06:10,720
Greetings, Princess.

102
00:06:11,040 --> 00:06:13,680
What does my audience with my mother have to do with you?

103
00:06:13,680 --> 00:06:14,960
That's not true.

104
00:06:15,560 --> 00:06:17,600
The Princess coming to our Great Jin for marriage

105
00:06:17,600 --> 00:06:20,320
is actually laying the foundation for the alliance between our two countries.

106
00:06:20,320 --> 00:06:23,560
And the core of the alliance involves a trade.

107
00:06:23,560 --> 00:06:25,600
Northern Di is rich in petroleum,

108
00:06:25,600 --> 00:06:27,080
which is an excellent fuel.

109
00:06:27,080 --> 00:06:28,360
This time, our Great Jin

110
00:06:28,360 --> 00:06:29,960
is exactly here to establish

111
00:06:29,960 --> 00:06:32,200
a long-term petroleum trade relationship with Northern Di.

112
00:06:32,200 --> 00:06:34,040
As the Vice Minister of Revenue,

113
00:06:34,040 --> 00:06:36,560
leading the trade is exactly my duty.

114
00:06:36,560 --> 00:06:38,880
Therefore, the alliance between our two countries

115
00:06:38,880 --> 00:06:41,000
is related to me.

116
00:06:44,159 --> 00:06:45,560
Mu Jiuyun,

117
00:06:45,880 --> 00:06:48,280
today is your day to die.

118
00:06:50,200 --> 00:06:52,720
[Speaks Northern Di] Daughter, what's wrong with you?

119
00:06:52,720 --> 00:06:53,440
What?

120
00:06:53,440 --> 00:06:56,240
[Speaks Northern Di] I'm asking you, what's wrong?

121
00:06:56,240 --> 00:06:58,480
The Princess is from Northern Di,

122
00:06:58,480 --> 00:07:01,040
but she doesn't seem to understand the Northern Di language.

123
00:07:01,040 --> 00:07:02,080
Oh no.

124
00:07:02,360 --> 00:07:03,520
For the past half year,

125
00:07:03,520 --> 00:07:05,120
I've only been focusing on alchemy and revenge.

126
00:07:05,120 --> 00:07:08,160
I thought I could kill Gu Licheng and his wife on my wedding day.

127
00:07:08,160 --> 00:07:11,420
I didn't have time to learn the Northern Di language at all.

128
00:07:12,840 --> 00:07:15,880
I just heard His Majesty the King of Northern Di say

129
00:07:15,880 --> 00:07:18,160
that the Princess has become obedient and sensible recently.

130
00:07:18,160 --> 00:07:20,760
But as far as my wife and I know,

131
00:07:20,760 --> 00:07:21,960
that is not the case.

132
00:07:26,240 --> 00:07:27,200
Princess,

133
00:07:27,600 --> 00:07:28,680
the other day,

134
00:07:28,680 --> 00:07:31,320
you tried to kill us twice

135
00:07:31,320 --> 00:07:32,360
for no reason.

136
00:07:32,360 --> 00:07:33,159
Why?

137
00:07:33,159 --> 00:07:34,440
Is there such a thing?

138
00:07:38,080 --> 00:07:40,760
Your Majesties, this is a matter of great importance.

139
00:07:40,760 --> 00:07:43,320
I would never dare to commit the crime of deceiving the sovereign

140
00:07:43,320 --> 00:07:44,920
by slandering the Princess.

141
00:07:46,240 --> 00:07:49,640
But if the Princess in front of us is an impostor,

142
00:07:50,280 --> 00:07:52,520
I dare not sit by and watch

143
00:07:52,800 --> 00:07:54,400
bandits cause trouble

144
00:07:54,760 --> 00:07:57,320
and ruin the alliance between our two countries.

145
00:07:57,320 --> 00:08:00,400
Then according to you, Gu,

146
00:08:01,200 --> 00:08:03,400
you suspect the Princess is a fake.

147
00:08:19,120 --> 00:08:19,480
Baorui,

148
00:08:19,480 --> 00:08:19,680
Bo.

149
00:08:24,720 --> 00:08:26,120
Zijian strengthens his character.

150
00:08:26,120 --> 00:08:26,400
Quan Xuhang,

151
00:08:26,400 --> 00:08:27,400
Kun, Quan Xuhang.

152
00:08:27,680 --> 00:08:28,410
Quan Yulong,

153
00:08:29,000 --> 00:08:29,930
Licheng, Lefei.

154
00:08:30,280 --> 00:08:30,600
Yunlong, Yinyu, Jia, Guangjing,

155
00:08:30,600 --> 00:08:32,460
Yunlong, Yinyu, Jia, Guangjing.

156
00:08:34,480 --> 00:08:34,760
Luo, Xiaocong, Linxun, Bo,

157
00:08:34,760 --> 00:08:35,000
Luo, Xiaocong, Linxun, Bo.
